            "title": "港股開市︱初段靠穩 恒指微升1點報20598點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">華爾街股市昨晚造好，雖然未惠及外圍中概股，但港股今早開市初段仍靠穩。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數開市報20598點，升1點或0.01%。恒生科技指數開報4926點，跌3點或0.07%；國企指數以7566點開市，升不足1點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股個別發展，阿里巴巴(09988)開報96.95元，跌0.62%；騰訊(00700)開報416.2元，跌0.38%；美團(03690)開報152.8元，升1.26%。滙控(00005)開報80.5元，升0.37%；友邦(01299)開報52元，跌1.89%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-172016__source-web_00005.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-172016__source-web_00005.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">傳京東(09618)再度研究收購德國電子產品零售商Ceconomy；京東今早開報154.7元，跌1.15%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">強勢股小米(01810)今早則開報39.8元，微升0.38%；中芯(00981)開報44.75元，升0.11%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">希瑪醫療(03309)發盈警，但表明擬恢復派2024年度股息；該股今早開報1.9元，跌1.04%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"智雲健康官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/09955-web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"智雲健康官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/09955-web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">智雲健康官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">智雲健康(09955)發自願公告，表示已通過接入DeepSeek提升智雲大腦；該股今早應聲彈14.91%，以1.85元開市。</p>\n</div>",
